comment.fullscreenwindowed.enableFullscreenWindowe=Enable Fullscreen Windowed (replaces Minecraft Fullscreen)
comment.fullscreenwindowed.fullscreenmonito=Indicates which monitor (1-based) to use for fullscreen windowed mode. Use 0 for the default behavior of maximizing on the active monitor.
comment.fullscreenwindowed.enableAdvancedFeature=To use any of the features in the "advanced" section, set this to true.
